@startuml
title Facade

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: Provide a unified, simpler interface to a subsystem.

**Use when**: Reduce complexity; provide an entry point.

**Key participants**: Facade, Subsystem classes.
endlegend

class Facade {
  +operation()
}

class SubsystemA {
  +a1()
}
class SubsystemB {
  +b1()
}
class SubsystemC {
  +c1()
}

Facade ..> SubsystemA
Facade ..> SubsystemB
Facade ..> SubsystemC

class Client
Client ..> Facade
@enduml